{"tid":2462421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"釣獲大魚被勸放生　釣魚郎與2漢爭執失足墮海","createTime":"2021-03-26T03:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T04:53:17.000Z","uid":7179,"like":91,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"f8bb2e0a2fa042bae4ee13b42761a6bda0231d1b","tid":2462421,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:52:34.000Z","msg":"今日(26日)凌晨零時許，一名姓楊(50歲)釣魚郎，在尖沙咀天星碼頭釣到大魚，2名旁觀男子建議放生回大海，楊斷言拒絕，雙方發生爭執。期間，事主遭對方出言恐嚇及推撞，繼而失足墮海，2男隨即逃去無蹤，楊自行游返岸上報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，楊男並無受傷，乘警車返警署助查，案件列「刑事恐嚇」及「普通襲擊」，交油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝2名涉案男子。他們年約30至40歲，其中1名男子身穿迷彩風衣及牛仔褲，另1男子身穿黑色風衣及黑色長褲。<br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b34717308110c3a44b0fd03ab5561238161bf1","tid":2462421,"uid":41888,"like":99,"dislike":5,"score":94,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"釣細魚就話放生姐<br />\n釣大魚都要放生咁on9"},{"pid":"2775dc7c120605f59c072129605db5f79869b109","tid":2462421,"uid":38416,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9f09b0c81a1a36a6052a13db07573eb85ff02d","tid":2462421,"uid":7043,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"on9釣魚都要俾人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3af82d56835c8366f9d81c07136757aa059851d","tid":2462421,"uid":39780,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"2775dc7c120605f59c072129605db5f79869b109","tid":2462421,"uid":38416,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25759e121855ead78365b24acd1a418ae849f6c8","tid":2462421,"uid":37389,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:54:47.000Z","ms